{"tid":1474860,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[分化mode]政府又用錢分化啦","createTime":"2019-08-15T10:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:31:20.000Z","uid":45788,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2c3947a0b21bd015f83fca59539fcff6319de5","tid":1474860,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"1705 #政府跨部門記招<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波發言於記招發言。他預計本港未來經濟會繼續疲弱，社會示威事件會令經濟更加下滑。<br />\n<br />\n以下為他提出的「撐企業，保就業，舒民困」措施要點：<br />\n－不同中小企可豁免數十類政府收費；<br />\n－批發市場租用地獲減租；<br />\n－向微小企業或新企業提供九成信貸擔保；<br />\n－優化中小企融資計劃；<br />\n－擴寬資助範圍；<br />\n－推展小型工程資助及計劃；<br />\n－僱員特別津貼及培訓計劃；<br />\n－薪俸稅及利得稅調升退稅金額；<br />\n－＄2500中小學生津貼；<br />\n－基層人士公屋免收一個月租金；<br />\n－基層人士公屋減收電費；<br />\n－N無人士生活津貼<br />\n<br />\n#RTHK<br />\n<br />\n你見唔見到有個共同點呀<br />\n<br />\n就係個受惠人都係中游派咋<br />\n好快就有一堆post屌政府冇派俾我地<br />\n之後五毛就會煽動我地去屌佢地架啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但請記住，不分化</span><br />\n點應對？其實根本wfc就夠<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反嘅都會反,撐嘅都會撐，唔理嘅都唔會理</span><br />\n政府轉打經濟牌不意外<br />\n但仆你個街出手出得咁孤寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n派得個2500，仲要唔知幾時先有<br />\n<del>係咪冇錢派啊？係我就沽港紙啦</del><br />\n<br />\n你當香港人乞衣呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議冷處理<br />\n文宣最好可以陰謀化咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n817 818見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5aa25d66cb5729269df39ac297c06e2cf96597a","tid":1474860,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"b829c404b28059e34094091f3e54316b429b258f","tid":1474860,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"香港人絕對唔缺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過照派，我要完繼續示威<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借推，大學生請幫個忙填問卷籌錢比612人道支援基金。<br />\n<br />\n問卷link： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=f85d4ad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6</a><br />\n<br />\n原post：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430200</a>"},{"pid":"0d847dc5129b86bedac57e6f9967384efdbb4d33","tid":1474860,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"計下大部分去左邊先啦"},{"pid":"5486c6d6f85fb1a658cb4a2001daa0a0f5e6f751","tid":1474860,"uid":19476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:10:11.000Z","msg":"收完錢繼續反"},{"pid":"09b690916011c3805b4d0b425d4385a6a39c5aaf","tid":1474860,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"ON9 有邊樣野係比我地?<br />\n咪又係比每日150<br />\n點會分化到"},{"pid":"b85db048d0d53e4f19461f5700ae3b5fe43f1f91","tid":1474860,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"派到手上時解放軍都未入到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ab960994588daf75b8f6e25f7dfe39a10f59ca","tid":1474860,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d847dc5129b86bedac57e6f9967384efdbb4d33","tid":1474860,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"計下大部分去左邊先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"中產/藍/普通家庭/蝗<br />\n<br />\n反開都係反<br />\n撐開都係撐"},{"pid":"0d0c70d08b75682b35f7d810556c0faebcae7694","tid":1474860,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b690916011c3805b4d0b425d4385a6a39c5aaf","tid":1474860,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-1